  <p>
    <span data-translate="about.description_part_1">I'm a versatile Software Developer currently based in Bochum,
      Germany.</span>
    <span data-translate="about.description_part_2">I love learning, experiencing and discovering new things. And I also
      have a passion for coding! 🚀</span>
    <span data-translate="about.description_part_3">I have had a lot of experience from small to big projects in the
      university, different companies or just doing them for fun from the comfort of my home.</span>
    <span data-translate="about.description_part_4">Projects that span from web, app, game to even AI development. 📈
      All of them brought me joy by letting my mind work, trying to figure out what was causing that pesky error or how
      I can make the code run faster and look prettier.</span>
    <span data-translate="about.description_part_5">I really enjoy coding riddles that get me thinking 🤔, and when I
      solve them, it's the best feeling ever!</span>
    <span data-translate="about.description_part_6">If you have a challenge for me, bring it on and don't hesitate to
      contact me! 📩</span>
  </p>

